  "texts": [
    "The images in PatternNet were sourced from Google Earth imagery or obtained via the Google Map API for specific US cities.",
    "Figure 6 displays the different image categories.",
    "Eurosat datasetThe EuroSAT dataset covers 13 spectral bands and consists of 10 distinct classes.",
    "This dataset contains 27,000 images, with each of the 10 classes consisting of 2,000 to 3,000 images.",
    "The images are in the form of patches, with each patch measuring 64 x 64 pixels."
